<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٥٩٨ - لَا أَدْرِي نِصْفَ الْعِلْمِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مِنْ كَلامِ الشَّعْبِيِّ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٥٩٩ - لَا بَأْسَ بِالذَّوَاقِ عِنْدَ الْمُشْتَرِي<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>لَيْسَ بِحَدِيثٍ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٦٠٠ - لَا تَتَمَارَضُوا فَتَمْرَضُوا وَلا تَحْفِرُوا قُبُورَكُمْ فَتَمُوتُوا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَرَدَ فِي السُّنَّةِ فِي الْجُمْلَةِ وَإِنْ أُنْكِرَ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>